<h2>Gum sores, Soreness or burning inside of mouth and White patches inside mouth</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms gum sores, soreness or burning inside of mouth and white patches inside mouth including Canker sores, Thrush (infants and children), and Allergic reaction.</p>
<p>There  are 8 conditions  associated with gum sores, soreness or burning inside of mouth and white patches inside mouth. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
